Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要穿这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别挑肥捡瘦的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喏 快瞧 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好土{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我自己穿咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还保留着这种生理现象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就死了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,------------
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找了午饭给你吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这叫午饭?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人的话就是圣旨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神器啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神器要尊敬主人 为主人奉献
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为主人的手脚工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要学会主动斟茶递水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想斟茶也没东西给你斟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准顶嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要顺从
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会秃啦
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.05,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}快住手 你这烂猫\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还以为当神明的都会做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果是漫无目的地在城里乱转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是避人耳目 在附近祠堂的角落里缩成一团睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日用品也是从垃圾堆捡来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs34\bord0\pos(958,308)\c&H3C3680&}外派电话 夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普及活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但完全没人来委托啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是神明?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那眼神是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识见识我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正中雅宋_GBK\fs40\c&H000000&\bord0\fsp8\3a&HA0\pos(467,260)}被招来的灾厄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和说要上供食物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这感召力如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这完全就是敲诈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完之后 务必要实现我的愿望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定好点什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 水要三杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非{\rsymbol}…{\r}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗你们不是人类 其他人应该看不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是不会被看到 而是不容易引起注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实他们都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反过来问你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有多少女服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不准看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔{\rsymbol}…{\r}两个?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 有四个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和雪音就像被你看漏的两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被当做了背景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一旦被认知 就会作为人类共存于意识中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很快又会被忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这城市里擦身而过的人 你也没全部记住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们由于是彼岸的住民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您二位胃口还真是不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,供奉之物不能剩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是铁则
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子会吃坏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明不蹲大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 那个人实在是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那啥{\rsymbol}…{\r}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一歧日和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我日和就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和跟那个是什么关系
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.76,0:06:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}这些糖给我包一下\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心变成了会灵魂出窍的体质
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.81,0:06:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}这个{\rsymbol}…{\r}\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想让夜斗帮忙治好
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}为什么不行\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.83,0:06:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}这不是免费的吗\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个{\rsymbol}…{\r}雪音君为什么{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为夜斗的神器之前 是怎么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之知道自己死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回过神来时 就在那家伙手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活着时的事情 完全想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后也不知该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你{\rsymbol}…{\r}是刚才那只鱼干小偷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君 你喜欢猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猫好可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音 你刚才想了限制级的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了雪音 我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明和神器是一心同体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心中邪念的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作为主人{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是会感受到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈?这家伙说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个{\rsymbol}…{\r}一心同体是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青春期的小鬼真让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呆子是什么意思
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}我的事你懂个屁啊\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}想干架吗 你这色小鬼 啊?\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真烦死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是会实现别人愿望的神明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好 我是快捷便宜又放心的外派神明夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音 有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的委托呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么也一起过来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意见的话就想办法治好我的体质
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假装委托 想要暗算我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东风若吹起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,务使庭香乘风来 枯枝满梅花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纵失主 亦勿忘春日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是菅原道真的和歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学问之神{\fscx200}—{\fscx100}天神大人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 认出来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位活幽灵小姐真是博学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这歌很老了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教科书上有教过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋了 著作权怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个只保持到死后50年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好有神明范儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在太庄严了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 夜斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp0\bord1.5}\h             Yuki                 Setsu\N{\r}名为雪 器为雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唤作雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音君 你刚刚成为神器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神器不必叩拜我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:09:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在自身侍奉的神明面前叩拜其他神明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乃失礼之行径
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦请牢记
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有好多巫女在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是步喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是南喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是实喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是望喻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天神姐妹组合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们啊 都是我的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,养活她们很费力的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的神明就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 找我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs30\bord0\1a&H70\c&H000000&\org(745,592)\frx0\fry9\frz357.866\pos(964,273)}希望能考上志愿的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs30\bord0\1a&H70\c&H000000&\org(398,699)\frx0\fry8\frz1.634\pos(641,146)}第一志愿\N希望大家都能考上高中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs30\bord0\1a&H70\c&H000000&\frx0\fry8\org(165,687)\pos(311,531)\frz2.286}希望中考能够考上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,705)}啊 我最近很忙嘛 因为是考试季
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望找人帮我斩个妖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你擅自在我家神社睡觉的事我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你加入我的天满集团也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你分店店长做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要自己的神社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我这只有大钞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能找开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 那些够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贫富差距都蔓延到这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说世道不公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这不是有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 劳你带路了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公 真喻来此时日尚浅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带路还应请其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔 可是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}不是假币吧\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真喻很熟悉夜斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伴音!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是伴音 是真喻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伴音 你{\rsymbol}…{\r}竟然抱了这么个大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真喻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前曾做过夜斗先生的神器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当初工作方面如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好好完成委托吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣食住行方面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真是居无定所无职无业的运动衫男?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是居无定所无职无业的 自称是神明的运动衫男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少捧一捧前任主人啊 伴音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真喻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别用过去的名字叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我碰一下就牢骚满腹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却跑来当老头子的烟管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你掉钱眼里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不跟着你 跟着谁都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你{\rsymbol}…{\r}你们原来是恋人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原夫妇吗 闹得相当僵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么 反正很僵啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}脏死了是什么意思\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别靠近我
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}有种你再说一遍\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们法庭上见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您找夜斗是委托除妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妖是如此邪恶的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要消灭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人心若冷天亦冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫日和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过分介入这边的事可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这些人总是多愁善感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前几天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人供上了一个有些奇怪的匾额
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord0\1a&H50\fn方正准圆_GBK\fsp0\frz0\c&H000000&\pos(413,364)}为了天国的朋友\N一定要考上大学\N{\fscx470}\h{\fscx100}夏希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调查过发现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经死去两人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这附近常有时化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是被循其而来的妖凭依 生了心魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道真大人为此倍感心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里施加了结界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但人带着心魔出入{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难完全净化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命如此宝贵 真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 只要消灭那个凭依人的妖就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人死掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想做些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想死的家伙去死就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是一如既往地渣到惊人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说 没有刚才那样说话的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会想到自杀的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就被心魔所占 连神器都做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是死掉的 还是活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都无药可救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 闪人咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 订金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她一个人走掉 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是第一次工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唤器之时则来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唤名之时则回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想死的家伙去死就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不想工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但上了大学 也没什么想做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寿司卷踢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不原谅附在人身上作恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伙{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伴{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一半是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带到彼岸去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过尾巴断了会死的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那边老实呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪音 接下来的道口才是正戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一志愿测定为E
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这下不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来彼岸就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好哦 很好哦
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.97,0:18:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34}很好哦 很好哦\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斩掉那只妖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别临阵退缩哦 雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦 很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丰苇原之中津国中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒乱无度的彼岸之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾 夜斗神显圣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此雪器斩碎降服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将业障重重之秽迹{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽数祓除!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:18:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\bord1.5\fsp0}Yuki{\fscx980}\h\N{\r}雪 行了 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才的斩击太过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然说想死的家伙去死就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但还是来救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是 不想让他在这些家伙面前死得轻于鸿毛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再痛苦再难过 都要好好感受生命之重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会想到自杀的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就被心魔所占 连神器都做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都这么年轻稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说并非自杀{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那神器们都是仍渴望活着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这些人面前轻生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜斗无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色鬼雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 做了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是刚才那些粉末进到眼睛里了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这个很要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要揉眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日和 冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下要深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸吸呼 来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吸吸呼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少能暖和点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天呢 嘛{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为初次工作 你表现得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:21:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
