Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:30.36,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}君の名前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:33.90,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}何があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:36.50,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}必ず呼ぶから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:52.49,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}君はぎざぎざハートの持ち主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:57.91,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}触れるものは何でも傷つけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:03.17,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}世界のすべてを睨みつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:05.93,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}その目は言うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.93,0:23:08.58,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}僕はここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.58,0:23:13.56,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}誰かが笑ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:16.42,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}だから引いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:18.91,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}その境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:24.10,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}それなら 私が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:27.55,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}その手を引く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:33.11,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}連れてくから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:39.22,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}言えないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:44.42,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}この手を強く握って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:46.38,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:54.59,ed_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}君はもうひとりじゃないんだって
